  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223740/extras/5909d351d97cdabae503fc9a3fe635de.poster.avif?t=1753898806\" width=600 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223740/extras/5909d351d97cdabae503fc9a3fe635de.webm?t=1753898806\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223740/extras/5909d351d97cdabae503fc9a3fe635de.mp4?t=1753898806\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Fire in the Dark is a <strong>multiplayer-only</strong> isometric arena shooter in which you can invite a friend to play against you. In a medieval fantasy small city, you become two witches facing each others in a duel at night. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223740/extras/56e921663d38c9ed66bc6e99e19f24df.poster.avif?t=1753898806\" width=450 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223740/extras/56e921663d38c9ed66bc6e99e19f24df.webm?t=1753898806\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223740/extras/56e921663d38c9ed66bc6e99e19f24df.mp4?t=1753898806\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Play with the shadows and hide in bushes, chase down your opponent to defeat him and prove who's best! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223740/extras/e8fd6cac8433fd23586e0c420d5f76f8.poster.avif?t=1753898806\" width=600 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223740/extras/e8fd6cac8433fd23586e0c420d5f76f8.webm?t=1753898806\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223740/extras/e8fd6cac8433fd23586e0c420d5f76f8.mp4?t=1753898806\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Use fireballs to deal damage, kindle up torches or burn down bushes! <br>Alternatively, rely on frostbolts to slow down your enemy and extinguish light sources in order to discreetly hide and wait for the right occasion to strike!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223740/extras/1466b7e450255cb5535085fd8a2eeb21.poster.avif?t=1753898806\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223740/extras/1466b7e450255cb5535085fd8a2eeb21.webm?t=1753898806\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223740/extras/1466b7e450255cb5535085fd8a2eeb21.mp4?t=1753898806\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223740/extras/5909d351d97cdabae503fc9a3fe635de.poster.avif?t=1753898806\" width=600 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223740/extras/5909d351d97cdabae503fc9a3fe635de.webm?t=1753898806\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223740/extras/5909d351d97cdabae503fc9a3fe635de.mp4?t=1753898806\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Fire in the Dark is a <strong>multiplayer-only</strong> isometric arena shooter in which you can invite a friend to play against you. In a medieval fantasy small city, you become two witches facing each others in a duel at night. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223740/extras/56e921663d38c9ed66bc6e99e19f24df.poster.avif?t=1753898806\" width=450 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223740/extras/56e921663d38c9ed66bc6e99e19f24df.webm?t=1753898806\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223740/extras/56e921663d38c9ed66bc6e99e19f24df.mp4?t=1753898806\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Play with the shadows and hide in bushes, chase down your opponent to defeat him and prove who's best! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223740/extras/e8fd6cac8433fd23586e0c420d5f76f8.poster.avif?t=1753898806\" width=600 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223740/extras/e8fd6cac8433fd23586e0c420d5f76f8.webm?t=1753898806\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223740/extras/e8fd6cac8433fd23586e0c420d5f76f8.mp4?t=1753898806\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Use fireballs to deal damage, kindle up torches or burn down bushes! <br>Alternatively, rely on frostbolts to slow down your enemy and extinguish light sources in order to discreetly hide and wait for the right occasion to strike!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223740/extras/1466b7e450255cb5535085fd8a2eeb21.poster.avif?t=1753898806\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223740/extras/1466b7e450255cb5535085fd8a2eeb21.webm?t=1753898806\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223740/extras/1466b7e450255cb5535085fd8a2eeb21.mp4?t=1753898806\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
